OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777299067
OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle's owner reveals club's
OL,4,C#10.5 million debt
OL,6,FPlymouth Argyle's owner Simon Hallett
OL,7,Fadmits the club's financial security
OL,8,Frelies on selling its best players
OL,9,Fafter revealing it had plunged more
OL,10,Fthan #10.5 million into the red.
OL,12,FThe Pilgrims made a small profit last
OL,13,Fseason but escalating costs have
OL,14,Fincreased debt, with the chairman
OL,15,Fhaving to invest a further #15 million
OL,16,Fof his personal fortune into the club.
OL,18,FMr Hallett believes the financiail
OL,19,Fsustainability of the club relies on
OL,20,Frecruitment, developing players who
OL,21,Fcan then be sold at a profit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
