OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777299067
OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle's owner reveals club's
OL,4,C#10.5 million debt
OL,6,FHe spoke to ITV News after addressing
OL,7,Ffans at a forum at Home Park - in the
OL,8,Fweek 18 people were made redundant at
OL,9,Fthe club.
OL,11,FHe said: "Our job is to replace them
OL,12,F(the players). People didn't want to
OL,13,Fsee Ryan Hardie go, and Ryan was one
OL,14,Fof my favourite ever players at
OL,15,FArgyle. I didn't want Ryan to go, but
OL,16,Fare we still talking about Ryan? No,
OL,17,Fwe are talking about Lorent Tolaj, Bim
OL,18,FPepple and Owen Oseni.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777299067
OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle's owner reveals club's
OL,4,C#10.5 million debt
OL,6,F"We have three strikers who have
OL,7,Fscored double digit goals this season
OL,8,F- and noboby knew who Bim or Owen was
OL,9,F(previously).
OL,11,F"We have done a good job using data,
OL,12,Fusing the recruitment team to unearth
OL,13,Fvery good value players. That's really
OL,14,Fwhat our job has to be. It will always
OL,15,Fbe difficult selling successful
OL,16,Fplayers, but that's the way to
OL,17,Fsustainability."
OL,19,FMr Hallett says the fragile state of
OL,20,Fthe English Football League is not
OL,21,Fsustainable and things have to change.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777299067
OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle's owner reveals club's
OL,4,C#10.5 million debt
OL,6,FHe added: "So, football is very good
OL,7,Fvalue and it is a real problem,
OL,8,Fparticularly at the moment, when your
OL,9,Fcost prices are set by government
OL,10,Fpolicy or whatever is going on in the
OL,11,Fworld, but we have got to set prices
OL,12,Ffor the population of Plymouth.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,434,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1777299067
OL,3,CPlymouth Argyle's owner reveals club's
OL,4,C#10.5 million debt
OL,6,F"Electricity prices are going up in a
OL,7,Fway that it is very, very hard to
OL,8,Frespond to. It is a problem for all
OL,9,Ffootball clubs - we all want to offer
OL,10,Fgood value, but when costs are going
OL,11,Fup and being driven up by things that
OL,12,Fare not local to Plymouth, not local
OL,13,Fto Devon and Cornwall, it is a real
OL,14,Fproblem."
OL,16,FAt the forum Mr Hallett and new CEO
OL,17,FPaul Berne assured fans the club's
OL,18,Fplaying budget of #10 million - this
OL,19,Fseason the seventh best in League 1 -
OL,20,Fwould remain for the next campaign.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
